371
00:43:37,041 --> 00:43:40,605
Forse.

372
00:43:40,625 --> 00:43:41,164
Che cosa vuoi?

373
00:43:41,826 --> 00:43:42,565
Intanto voglio entrare.

374
00:43:43,347 --> 00:43:44,728
